1
00:00:00,270 --> 00:00:01,570
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,570 --> 00:00:03,380
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,380 --> 00:00:05,210
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:07,610 --> 00:00:08,810
(Episode 41)

5
00:00:10,620 --> 00:00:11,650
It's a match.

6
00:00:12,120 --> 00:00:14,950
The two prints belong
to the same person.

7
00:00:15,220 --> 00:00:17,220
- Darn.
- You!

8
00:00:17,390 --> 00:00:18,460
Min Jun!

9
00:00:48,790 --> 00:00:49,790
Baek Jin Ju.

10
00:00:52,090 --> 00:00:53,260
Baek Jin Ju!

11
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,800
I'm sorry.

12
00:01:36,940 --> 00:01:38,900
I'm sorry it took me so long
to recognize you.

13
00:01:41,170 --> 00:01:43,810
I promised we'd be together
every moment,

14
00:01:44,580 --> 00:01:46,910
but I left you
to face those flames alone.

15
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:49,880
I'm sorry I let you cry alone
for all that time.

16
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:55,290
Even with you right here
in front of me,

17
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:57,960
I was so lost.

18
00:02:00,060 --> 00:02:02,990
This moment.
The moment you'd return?

19
00:02:04,460 --> 00:02:06,000
I desperately longed for it,

20
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,530
but I never dared dream
it would happen.

21
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,240
But now...

22
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:15,840
I won't lose my way again.
I'll never let you go.

23
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:25,620
I'm...

24
00:02:31,490 --> 00:02:32,560
I'm Chloe.

25
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:43,970
I'm not Baek Jin Ju.

26
00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:46,740
I said I'm Chloe.

27
00:02:50,140 --> 00:02:52,680
Jin Ju, come on.

28
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:55,510
I've already confirmed it all.

29
00:02:57,020 --> 00:02:59,050
Please, don't do this.

30
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:02,590
Please!

31
00:03:04,490 --> 00:03:05,520
Wake up from your dream,

32
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:08,030
from this delusion.

33
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:13,830
I've told you countless times
I'm not that dead woman.

34
00:03:15,930 --> 00:03:17,970
What will it take for you
to snap out of it?

35
00:03:18,340 --> 00:03:19,940
What do I have to do...

36
00:03:24,210 --> 00:03:25,310
to make you stop?

37
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:28,310
Jin Ju.

38
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:36,490
Please stop calling me that.

39
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,530
I'm sick of it.

40
00:03:42,730 --> 00:03:44,160
It's repulsive.

41
00:03:47,270 --> 00:03:49,130
Do you miss that dead woman
that much?

42
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:53,240
Is that why you're so desperate
to hold me like I'm her?

43
00:03:53,570 --> 00:03:54,840
If that's the case,

44
00:03:55,970 --> 00:03:58,810
just be honest
and say you want to sleep with me.

45
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,800
Jin Ju.

46
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:23,900
Baek Jin Ju!

47
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:28,870
Jin Ju.

48
00:04:29,810 --> 00:04:30,810
Jin Ju...

49
00:04:31,340 --> 00:04:32,740
Baek Jin Ju!

50
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,230
Min Jun...

51
00:05:26,330 --> 00:05:27,430
I'm...

52
00:05:28,530 --> 00:05:29,830
almost there.

53
00:05:31,870 --> 00:05:33,640
Just a little further,

54
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:36,470
and I'll get to see...

55
00:05:37,180 --> 00:05:40,010
Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na
destroy each other.

56
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,120
I'll be able to clear...

57
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:48,650
my father's name.

58
00:05:55,290 --> 00:05:57,230
I can't fall apart until then.

59
00:05:59,660 --> 00:06:01,400
I can't let my cover
be blown like this.

60
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,610
What's going on?

61
00:06:13,110 --> 00:06:15,110
Why is Jin Ju living as Chloe?

62
00:06:15,810 --> 00:06:18,480
You called me out here,
but you're not making any sense.

63
00:06:18,620 --> 00:06:20,180
Did she lose her memory
in the accident?

64
00:06:20,820 --> 00:06:23,990
Did you trick her after the accident
into living as Chloe?

65
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:27,730
Mr. Park, please calm down.

66
00:06:28,030 --> 00:06:29,890
Please!

67
00:06:38,340 --> 00:06:39,340
Please...

68
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:43,070
Please, just tell me the truth.

69
00:06:44,610 --> 00:06:46,440
Jin Ju is alive,

70
00:06:47,250 --> 00:06:48,680
but I can't seem to reach her.

71
00:06:49,050 --> 00:06:51,020
I can't leave her alone again,

72
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:55,250
and I can't bear the thought
that she might slip...

73
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,990
even further away.

74
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:07,200
Jin Ju was my dream
and my every breath.

75
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:10,000
She was my everything.

76
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:14,370
And now I know she's alive.

77
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:17,070
After all this time,
she came back into my life.

78
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:20,240
Please help me get her back.

79
00:07:21,710 --> 00:07:22,710
Please.

80
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,050
Please!

81
00:07:28,620 --> 00:07:29,690
Help me.

82
00:07:42,770 --> 00:07:44,540
You want her back that badly?

83
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:48,540
All right, then.

84
00:07:49,710 --> 00:07:52,310
You'll have to start
by fixing what went wrong.

85
00:07:52,940 --> 00:07:56,280
And you, Mr. Park,
have to be the one to do it.

86
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:57,920
Of course,

87
00:07:58,350 --> 00:07:59,380
be careful...

88
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:02,820
not to drive my daughter
further away in the process.

89
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:05,660
That's right.

90
00:08:06,490 --> 00:08:08,030
That's all the advice...

91
00:08:09,790 --> 00:08:11,030
I can give you.

92
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:26,310
(Consultant, Chloe Lee)

93
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:39,520
Fix what went wrong?

94
00:08:41,660 --> 00:08:43,930
Why you came back as Chloe...

95
00:08:43,930 --> 00:08:46,430
and why you need to be her.

96
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:49,170
I'll start by figuring that out.

97
00:08:50,770 --> 00:08:52,940
If that's what it takes
to get you back,

98
00:08:55,470 --> 00:08:56,870
then that's where I'll start.

99
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:02,680
No matter who you are,
Jin Ju or Chloe,

100
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:07,620
I'll just love you from now on.

101
00:09:21,230 --> 00:09:24,200
It must be the fingerprint.

102
00:09:24,970 --> 00:09:27,200
The only thing
that could make him so sure...

103
00:09:28,410 --> 00:09:29,810
is the fingerprint.

104
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:32,710
Where did I slip up?

105
00:09:33,310 --> 00:09:36,150
Can I keep fooling him
just by denying it?

106
00:09:41,590 --> 00:09:43,150
Don't worry so much.

107
00:09:43,650 --> 00:09:45,220
He's a careful person.

108
00:09:46,290 --> 00:09:49,430
He won't cause trouble
by telling others you're Jin Ju.

109
00:09:52,230 --> 00:09:54,730
I thought I had completely
become Chloe.

110
00:09:56,800 --> 00:10:00,340
I can fool my would-be killers,
Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na.

111
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:04,610
But I guess I couldn't fool Min Jun,

112
00:10:06,140 --> 00:10:08,910
the one person who truly loves me.

113
00:10:10,410 --> 00:10:11,420
Right.

114
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:13,750
Jin Ju.

115
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,890
You could tell him
who you really are...

116
00:10:16,890 --> 00:10:18,620
and ask for his help.

117
00:10:23,130 --> 00:10:26,830
If I only wanted them
to be punished legally,

118
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:28,970
then he might be able to help.

119
00:10:30,430 --> 00:10:32,640
But when you're up
against Chairman Park Tae Ho,

120
00:10:32,940 --> 00:10:33,970
the law...

121
00:10:34,410 --> 00:10:35,910
is powerless.

122
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:41,210
That's why I'm going
to make Choi Yu Na...

123
00:10:41,850 --> 00:10:43,580
kill Park Tae Ho herself.

124
00:10:45,250 --> 00:10:46,920
With Park Tae Ho's blood
on her hands,

125
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:50,990
I'll turn Choi Yu Na into a murderer
and destroy her.

126
00:10:54,930 --> 00:10:56,360
Even Min Jun...

127
00:10:57,830 --> 00:11:00,970
would never help me
kill his own father.

128
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:05,600
Even if it means
breaking Min Jun's heart...

129
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:07,540
and trampling his feelings,

130
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:12,380
I'll see this through as Chloe
to the end.

131
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:28,830
Unbelievable.

132
00:11:33,660 --> 00:11:34,770
Let me get this straight.

133
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:39,200
You get duped by a con artist,
and this is what you say?

134
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:41,110
A fake identity?

135
00:11:41,910 --> 00:11:43,010
Well, it's...

136
00:11:43,610 --> 00:11:47,850
He was sure she was Kim Dan Hui,
not Kim Myung Hui.

137
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:49,850
So?

138
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:51,680
Are you proud of yourself
or something?

139
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:56,120
No one said that.
I'm the victim here too.

140
00:11:56,450 --> 00:11:58,360
Frankly, the con artist is to blame.

141
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,060
How am I to blame for being tricked?

142
00:12:00,420 --> 00:12:02,960
What was I supposed to do
when the lie felt so real?

143
00:12:04,100 --> 00:12:06,100
Are you sure
you weren't a willing participant?

144
00:12:06,530 --> 00:12:08,830
What? You're really pushing it.

145
00:12:08,930 --> 00:12:10,300
That's enough!

146
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:16,110
This is what happens
when you run wild.

147
00:12:16,610 --> 00:12:17,980
If you had stayed out of it,

148
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:20,910
the con artist
wouldn't have targeted you.

149
00:12:21,310 --> 00:12:23,580
You should've heard him out...

150
00:12:23,580 --> 00:12:25,850
and backed off
if something felt off.

151
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,750
Unbelievable.

152
00:12:28,090 --> 00:12:31,420
You were so desperate
to dig up dirt on Myung Hui...

153
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:33,690
that you couldn't think straight.

154
00:12:34,190 --> 00:12:37,360
When are you going to drop
this classless act?

155
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:40,200
Classless?

156
00:12:40,430 --> 00:12:44,940
What's the use of covering yourself
in designer clothes head to toe?

157
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:48,340
Your gutter-trash nature
is still the same.

158
00:12:48,570 --> 00:12:50,310
I'm not the only one
who came from the gutter.

159
00:12:50,810 --> 00:12:53,140
You and that tramp did too.

160
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:55,080
How are we the same?

161
00:12:56,180 --> 00:12:59,780
You're still stuck in the gutter,

162
00:12:59,950 --> 00:13:01,950
while Myung Hui and I
have risen above it.

163
00:13:03,450 --> 00:13:07,020
Show some class and act your status.

164
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,230
Sure.

165
00:13:08,530 --> 00:13:13,160
Look at you two,
all high and mighty now.

166
00:13:13,230 --> 00:13:15,630
Want a standing ovation?

167
00:13:15,730 --> 00:13:17,430
Why you...

168
00:13:18,140 --> 00:13:19,640
I swear...

169
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:22,570
Why do I even bother?

170
00:13:31,450 --> 00:13:32,650
Kim Dan Hui.

171
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:40,320
You still don't get it, do you?

172
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:45,960
Don't worry. I know what's going on.

173
00:13:46,460 --> 00:13:48,030
Kim Dan Hui, my foot.

174
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:51,300
I was fooled by a con man
and made it all up.

175
00:13:52,570 --> 00:13:55,170
You win this round.

176
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:08,990
She's admitting defeat this easily?

177
00:14:10,390 --> 00:14:11,390
No way.

178
00:14:12,020 --> 00:14:15,190
She's only pretending to admit it
while still being suspicious.

179
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:26,100
You want me to find Kim Dan Hui?

180
00:14:26,970 --> 00:14:29,240
Do you still believe that con man?

181
00:14:30,980 --> 00:14:35,710
A person can lie with words,
but not with their eyes.

182
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:39,880
I'm telling you, she was very shaken
by the name Kim Dan Hui.

183
00:14:41,690 --> 00:14:43,520
From the very beginning,

184
00:14:43,890 --> 00:14:46,720
my gut told me something was off
about that name.

185
00:14:47,260 --> 00:14:48,630
Your intuition sucks.

186
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:52,360
We'll see if my intuition sucks
after you look into it.

187
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:55,000
Hurry up and go find out.

188
00:14:55,430 --> 00:14:57,600
Where am I supposed to look?

189
00:14:57,800 --> 00:14:59,940
It's like finding a needle
in a haystack.

190
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:02,040
Finding her can't be easy.

191
00:15:02,340 --> 00:15:03,640
Are you kidding me?

192
00:15:04,170 --> 00:15:07,240
Do I have to spoon-feed you
every single thing?

193
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:09,350
Go to that con man,

194
00:15:09,350 --> 00:15:11,920
and if needed twist his arm
or break his legs.

195
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:15,450
Then find Kim Dan Hui,
the one adopted by that family.

196
00:15:16,950 --> 00:15:18,520
He was arrested by the police?

197
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:22,460
Yes. Woo Jin and I
were waiting outside...

198
00:15:22,530 --> 00:15:23,890
to hand him over to the police.

199
00:15:24,090 --> 00:15:26,830
But before we could make a move,
the police arrived.

200
00:15:26,930 --> 00:15:29,330
I don't know if their investigation
led them here...

201
00:15:29,530 --> 00:15:31,870
or if they already knew he was here.

202
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,800
I couldn't confirm which it was.

203
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:38,240
Still, now that he's been arrested,
he won't cause any more trouble.

204
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:40,080
But I can't let my guard down.

205
00:15:40,410 --> 00:15:43,150
I don't think Oh Jung Ran
has given up yet.

206
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:45,120
She might even go
to the police station...

207
00:15:45,380 --> 00:15:47,380
to dig for information.

208
00:15:47,890 --> 00:15:50,250
Keep an eye on Oh Jung Ran
and her driver for me.

209
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,420
Got it.

210
00:15:52,890 --> 00:15:55,960
I'll ask Woo Jin
to tail Mr. Song, too.

211
00:15:57,160 --> 00:15:59,660
He was arrested right in front
of the house?

212
00:16:00,060 --> 00:16:02,830
That's too weird
to be a coincidence.

213
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:10,140
He should've been arrested
before Oh Jung Ran dragged him in.

214
00:16:10,540 --> 00:16:13,410
Why did you let that filthy lowlife
set foot in my house?

215
00:16:16,110 --> 00:16:17,980
Make sure no rumors get out...

216
00:16:18,150 --> 00:16:21,290
about him trying
to scam Adele Group.

217
00:16:22,020 --> 00:16:25,360
And make sure the name Kim Dan Hui
never becomes a problem again.

218
00:16:27,460 --> 00:16:29,530
Not a single piece of information
can leak out.

219
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:32,630
Make sure everyone keeps
their mouths shut.

220
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:44,710
I told you to go find him now.

221
00:16:44,710 --> 00:16:46,680
But I can't.

222
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:49,880
He knows he's a wanted man.
If I were him, I'd be in hiding too.

223
00:16:50,350 --> 00:16:53,080
Why do you care so much
about a con man's lies?

224
00:16:53,150 --> 00:16:55,220
Just because he's a con man
doesn't mean he's always lying.

225
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:58,890
He's a con man
because all he does is lie.

226
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:03,130
Hyun Jun.

227
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:08,170
Are you just coming home from work?

228
00:17:08,470 --> 00:17:10,370
How's your hand?
Have you taken your medicine?

229
00:17:10,370 --> 00:17:11,770
Shouldn't you see a doctor again?

230
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:14,240
- I'm fine.
- You...

231
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:21,810
Don't you ever...

232
00:17:22,850 --> 00:17:24,580
pull a stunt like that
in front of me again.

233
00:17:25,080 --> 00:17:26,120
Understand?

234
00:17:28,990 --> 00:17:30,350
You're the one
who should never again...

235
00:17:31,390 --> 00:17:33,120
take my feelings so lightly.

236
00:17:34,190 --> 00:17:35,230
Next time,

237
00:17:36,090 --> 00:17:38,030
I won't stop at just my hand.

238
00:17:41,830 --> 00:17:43,830
Park Hyun Jun! How dare you...

239
00:17:45,840 --> 00:17:48,310
Come on, just leave him be.

240
00:17:50,940 --> 00:17:52,840
Give in a little.

241
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:56,780
To be blunt, what's the point
of gaining Adele if you lose him?

242
00:17:58,120 --> 00:18:00,580
It's better to convince him
to fight hard for succession...

243
00:18:00,580 --> 00:18:04,820
in exchange for letting him marry
the woman he loves.

244
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:07,960
Just let him...

245
00:18:08,430 --> 00:18:10,430
marry Chloe.

246
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:13,730
How can I approve a marriage
that's so obviously doomed?

247
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:17,500
How can I let him enter a marriage
where he's the only one invested?

248
00:18:18,270 --> 00:18:21,470
She could have ulterior motives
for marrying him without any love.

249
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:27,010
This thing with Chloe, or whatever,
is driving me insane!

250
00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:41,020
For crying out loud.
I almost lost my mind.

251
00:18:41,290 --> 00:18:42,290
What the...

252
00:18:42,890 --> 00:18:45,660
Hey, stop with the crazy eyes.

253
00:18:45,660 --> 00:18:47,830
If you're tired, just go to sleep.

254
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:50,630
You've been refusing to sleep
for days. My goodness.

255
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:53,940
- Good grief.
- This is killing me too.

256
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:55,740
The second I close my eyes,

257
00:18:56,340 --> 00:18:59,580
I see Jin Ju's ghost in front of me.
What am I supposed to do?

258
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:02,280
Chloe. That's her name.

259
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:05,850
She's not a ghost,
she's a real person.

260
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,550
What if she's...

261
00:19:08,090 --> 00:19:10,090
possessed by Jin Ju's ghost?

262
00:19:10,790 --> 00:19:12,590
What if that's why...

263
00:19:13,690 --> 00:19:15,590
she looks like Jin Ju to us?

264
00:19:17,530 --> 00:19:18,960
That's a terrifying thought.

265
00:19:19,030 --> 00:19:23,670
Honestly, you big baby.
You're such a coward.

266
00:19:23,970 --> 00:19:27,040
How do you survive
being so soft and naive?

267
00:19:27,040 --> 00:19:29,410
You drive me crazy!

268
00:19:32,540 --> 00:19:33,780
For crying out loud.

269
00:19:36,350 --> 00:19:38,250
Dad, are you still acting like this?

270
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:41,650
How many times do I have to tell you
she's not Baek Jin Ju?

271
00:19:42,390 --> 00:19:43,890
I know it's not her,

272
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:45,790
but I can...

273
00:19:46,190 --> 00:19:49,030
still clearly see Jin Ju's face
glaring at me that day.

274
00:19:49,530 --> 00:19:51,830
Her name's Chloe!

275
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,760
It reminds me of seven years ago.

276
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:57,830
What? What about seven years ago?

277
00:19:58,470 --> 00:20:02,240
Just stop it.
Let the dead go already.

278
00:20:04,580 --> 00:20:06,410
Why is she so touchy today?

279
00:20:07,180 --> 00:20:10,550
Fine, I give up.
Stay in bed for all I care.

280
00:20:11,720 --> 00:20:13,180
What a life this is.

281
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:21,960
Why did Dad even bring up something
from seven years ago?

282
00:20:23,060 --> 00:20:26,730
It's a one-of-a-kind,
award-winning matching set.

283
00:20:27,460 --> 00:20:28,470
Here you go.

284
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:33,240
Go ahead,
win Mr. Shin's heart with this gift.

285
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:35,410
No.

286
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:38,410
I didn't steal anything.

287
00:20:38,980 --> 00:20:40,310
It was Baek Jin Ju.

288
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:42,250
I liked Min Jun first.

289
00:20:42,250 --> 00:20:44,050
Jin Ju was the one
who got in the way.

290
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:48,520
I secured both Min Jun and Adele...

291
00:20:49,350 --> 00:20:51,390
through my own hard work.

292
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:57,830
If I win this competition,

293
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:01,060
I'll finally have it all.

294
00:21:03,630 --> 00:21:05,370
(Adele)

295
00:21:13,810 --> 00:21:15,650
Are you here
about what happened yesterday?

296
00:21:17,010 --> 00:21:18,180
Partly, yes,

297
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,720
but you're a lot different
than you were yesterday.

298
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:24,450
I was expecting you to harass me,
calling me by a dead woman's name.

299
00:21:26,520 --> 00:21:29,260
I'm sorry about yesterday. And...

300
00:21:30,730 --> 00:21:34,030
I'm sorry I used your fingerprint
without your permission.

301
00:21:34,970 --> 00:21:36,230
My fingerprint?

302
00:21:37,830 --> 00:21:38,870
Actually,

303
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:43,040
I wanted to compare yours
with Jin Ju's,

304
00:21:43,110 --> 00:21:44,980
so I sent both samples
to Hanguk University's...

305
00:21:44,980 --> 00:21:46,240
forensic science department.

306
00:21:47,410 --> 00:21:50,080
So it was the fingerprints.
I knew it.

307
00:21:50,650 --> 00:21:54,120
He must have sent them in
before I could switch mine.

308
00:21:55,020 --> 00:21:56,050
But...

309
00:21:56,620 --> 00:21:58,320
Forget about mine.

310
00:21:58,460 --> 00:22:01,060
How did you get
a dead woman's fingerprints?

311
00:22:02,030 --> 00:22:05,300
It was a long shot, but they
were lifted from Jin Ju's watch.

312
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:06,460
However,

313
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:09,130
I heard back from the processor.

314
00:22:12,970 --> 00:22:14,740
Because it had been seven years,

315
00:22:15,070 --> 00:22:17,240
there was an error
during the restoration process.

316
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:22,780
Is that why
you're acting so differently?

317
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:30,150
This way, you won't be on edge.

318
00:22:31,390 --> 00:22:33,220
It's the only way I could keep...

319
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:35,560
seeing you.

320
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:38,630
Why aren't you answering me?

321
00:22:40,330 --> 00:22:42,630
I thought it over one more time
before answering.

322
00:22:46,270 --> 00:22:47,900
I asked myself who you were.

323
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:55,780
From now on, I won't be confused
or have any doubts.

324
00:22:56,510 --> 00:22:58,420
Because you are,
without a doubt, Chloe.

325
00:22:59,650 --> 00:23:00,920
You're Jin Ju too,

326
00:23:01,690 --> 00:23:03,750
the Baek Jin Ju I love.

327
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:14,770
Just as I suspected,
it was the fingerprints.

328
00:23:16,130 --> 00:23:19,140
Luckily, he said it's an error
because the old prints degraded,

329
00:23:20,140 --> 00:23:22,440
but I need to know
whether that's true...

330
00:23:22,840 --> 00:23:23,970
or whether he's lying to me.

331
00:23:25,810 --> 00:23:27,940
Yes, I'm heading out right now.

332
00:23:30,010 --> 00:23:31,010
Right.

333
00:23:32,020 --> 00:23:34,380
He's a forensic science professor
at Hanguk University.

334
00:23:38,590 --> 00:23:41,220
A forensic science professor
at Hanguk University?

335
00:23:42,630 --> 00:23:46,830
The person Min Jun met
was also a professor from there.

336
00:23:51,030 --> 00:23:53,770
What? That con man got arrested?

337
00:23:54,100 --> 00:23:57,110
Mrs. Ok said she saw it happen
outside the gate,

338
00:23:57,340 --> 00:24:01,810
and that the police arrested him
as soon as he walked out.

339
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:04,580
- Right?
- Yes, that's correct.

340
00:24:05,220 --> 00:24:07,650
He's a con man,
so I followed him out...

341
00:24:07,650 --> 00:24:09,690
to make sure the gates were locked.

342
00:24:10,190 --> 00:24:13,720
Mr. Song was wondering
whether to look for him,

343
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:16,290
so I thought I'd let you know.

344
00:24:17,260 --> 00:24:21,230
But why are you looking
for that con man again?

345
00:24:22,330 --> 00:24:25,540
That's none of your business.
Get back to work.

346
00:24:26,570 --> 00:24:27,770
Yes, Ms. Oh.

347
00:24:31,070 --> 00:24:34,480
So he was arrested.
He's allowed visitors, right?

348
00:24:36,750 --> 00:24:38,650
Do you want to see him?

349
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:42,590
I'm going to make sure
one last time.

350
00:24:43,820 --> 00:24:47,460
There's definitely something
about that name, Kim Dan Hui.

351
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:54,100
You want to start working
at the gallery?

352
00:24:55,570 --> 00:24:56,570
Yes.

353
00:24:57,170 --> 00:24:59,400
Before Ms. Oh caused
all that trouble,

354
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:01,270
you told me
to take over the gallery...

355
00:25:01,500 --> 00:25:04,880
and prepare the funds
for Assemblyman Kwon.

356
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:08,180
Do you have enough for the deal?

357
00:25:09,380 --> 00:25:13,420
How much should I prepare
through the gallery, and how?

358
00:25:17,120 --> 00:25:19,820
There's no need to rush.

359
00:25:21,120 --> 00:25:22,130
Excuse me?

360
00:25:25,060 --> 00:25:27,160
But Assemblyman Kwon
will be waiting.

361
00:25:29,670 --> 00:25:33,200
We still have time,
so let's take it slow.

362
00:25:35,170 --> 00:25:37,640
My wife knows
the gallery business well,

363
00:25:39,540 --> 00:25:41,980
so let's discuss it with her
before moving forward.

364
00:25:42,950 --> 00:25:44,920
With Ms. Oh?

365
00:25:45,420 --> 00:25:46,750
She may cause trouble,

366
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:49,220
but she's been doing this
for a long time.

367
00:25:51,020 --> 00:25:52,660
Since this is an important matter,

368
00:25:55,130 --> 00:25:56,460
we should make use of her.

369
00:25:59,260 --> 00:26:01,260
Yes, I understand.

370
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:08,710
(Chairman's Office)

371
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:16,350
Why the sudden change of mind?

372
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:20,350
Could it be because of the person
Oh Jung Ran brought in?

373
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:24,320
Is he worried
about the name Kim Dan Hui?

374
00:26:31,090 --> 00:26:34,100
Darn, this is just my luck.

375
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:36,700
I get caught right after
getting involved with you people,

376
00:26:37,030 --> 00:26:40,200
and you track me down here just
to keep going on about Kim Dan Hui?

377
00:26:41,170 --> 00:26:42,940
I already told you
everything I know.

378
00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:44,710
What more do you want from me?

379
00:26:46,680 --> 00:26:47,910
You're nothing but a con man,

380
00:26:48,810 --> 00:26:50,050
and you took my money!

381
00:26:51,610 --> 00:26:54,020
You should at least tell me
what was a lie...

382
00:26:54,080 --> 00:26:56,050
and what was the truth.

383
00:26:56,790 --> 00:26:58,560
What part about Kim Dan Hui is true?

384
00:27:00,020 --> 00:27:01,190
Was she really adopted?

385
00:27:02,230 --> 00:27:03,230
Fine.

386
00:27:03,830 --> 00:27:07,800
Then either pay me more
or get me out of here.

387
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:10,070
Darn it. Just my luck.

388
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,440
After my uncle got sick,

389
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:15,510
they brought in that jinx
and lost everything.

390
00:27:15,570 --> 00:27:17,970
I got dragged down with them
for no good reason.

391
00:27:19,580 --> 00:27:21,880
So it's true she was adopted.

392
00:27:23,080 --> 00:27:24,210
And what's this
about her being sick?

393
00:27:25,450 --> 00:27:26,480
Tell me the truth.

394
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:30,020
What was wrong with her?

395
00:27:30,290 --> 00:27:32,460
I don't know!

396
00:27:36,930 --> 00:27:37,930
Come to think of it,

397
00:27:38,460 --> 00:27:41,160
I think I heard she went
to a nearby university hospital.

398
00:27:41,360 --> 00:27:42,370
Whatever!

399
00:27:42,670 --> 00:27:45,870
I have nothing more to say
about Kim Dan Hui,

400
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:48,370
so let's not see each other again.

401
00:27:49,140 --> 00:27:51,010
- You're bad news.
- Why you...

402
00:27:51,270 --> 00:27:52,280
We're done here.

403
00:27:53,980 --> 00:27:57,350
Where are you going?
Hey, we're not done talking!

404
00:27:57,450 --> 00:27:59,920
- Hey!
- Jung Ran, please.

405
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,790
You'll smash it.

406
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:06,090
That darn con artist.

407
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:08,160
See?

408
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:11,530
I told you we shouldn't have trusted
a con man and come all this way.

409
00:28:11,690 --> 00:28:13,960
He confirmed she was adopted
and that she was sick.

410
00:28:15,800 --> 00:28:17,330
She was treated
at a university hospital nearby.

411
00:28:17,330 --> 00:28:18,670
Find out where she lived...

412
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:21,810
and check the hospitals
for Kim Dan Hui.

413
00:28:22,070 --> 00:28:23,070
What?

414
00:28:25,040 --> 00:28:26,240
Since it's come to this,

415
00:28:26,810 --> 00:28:29,050
I need to know everything
about Kim Dan Hui.

416
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:41,020
Thank you for agreeing
to meet with me.

417
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:42,730
Not at all.

418
00:28:43,530 --> 00:28:46,160
Your fingerprint was used
in my study without your consent.

419
00:28:46,700 --> 00:28:49,830
It was my oversight
not to confirm it.

420
00:28:50,330 --> 00:28:52,800
It's only right for me
to apologize to you in person.

421
00:28:53,800 --> 00:28:55,740
I didn't come here to cause trouble.

422
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:59,140
I asked to meet with you
to confirm something.

423
00:28:59,710 --> 00:29:00,710
Confirm something?

424
00:29:02,250 --> 00:29:05,220
What were the results
of the fingerprint comparison?

425
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:07,880
And what did you report...

426
00:29:08,180 --> 00:29:10,220
to Director Park Min Jun
of the Adele Group?

427
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:15,790
I told him they were a match
and came from the same person.

428
00:29:19,730 --> 00:29:20,960
But later,

429
00:29:21,700 --> 00:29:25,570
I said there was an error
in developing the latent print...

430
00:29:26,370 --> 00:29:27,740
and that they weren't.

431
00:29:28,510 --> 00:29:31,570
So it really was an error?

432
00:29:33,310 --> 00:29:37,110
The problem was with the watch found
at the scene of the car explosion.

433
00:29:38,280 --> 00:29:39,750
We managed to lift
a fingerprint from it,

434
00:29:40,020 --> 00:29:42,390
but since it's been seven years,
it wasn't perfect.

435
00:29:43,220 --> 00:29:46,790
On re-evaluation, I concluded
it was a stretch to call it a match.

436
00:29:49,490 --> 00:29:50,490
I see.

437
00:29:52,130 --> 00:29:54,530
I understand. Thank you.

438
00:29:57,730 --> 00:30:00,140
You want me to meet
this Chloe person?

439
00:30:00,970 --> 00:30:03,170
Yes. Please meet with her
when she contacts you.

440
00:30:03,540 --> 00:30:06,280
Tell her there was an error
recovering the print,

441
00:30:06,280 --> 00:30:07,410
and the comparison showed...

442
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:10,250
they weren't a match.

443
00:30:10,910 --> 00:30:12,920
Are you asking me to lie?

444
00:30:13,650 --> 00:30:15,790
I'm doing this to protect someone
very important to me.

445
00:30:17,520 --> 00:30:19,320
I know this is a lot to ask.

446
00:30:28,130 --> 00:30:29,200
But please, help me.

447
00:30:40,840 --> 00:30:43,310
I should be going.

448
00:30:43,580 --> 00:30:47,250
Yes, thank you for understanding
our use of your fingerprint.

449
00:31:08,610 --> 00:31:09,610
Professor.

450
00:31:12,180 --> 00:31:13,710
Didn't we meet at Adele?

451
00:31:13,710 --> 00:31:16,050
Yes, we did. Please have a seat.

452
00:31:19,150 --> 00:31:21,720
It's about the person
you were just with.

453
00:31:22,390 --> 00:31:24,490
What did you talk about with Chloe?

454
00:31:24,820 --> 00:31:27,290
We spoke about the fingerprints.

455
00:31:27,820 --> 00:31:28,830
The fingerprints?

456
00:31:29,390 --> 00:31:30,390
Yes.

457
00:31:32,500 --> 00:31:34,560
Does that mean Min Jun...

458
00:31:36,970 --> 00:31:41,100
Did you compare Baek Jin Ju's
and Chloe's prints? And?

459
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,440
No, wait.

460
00:31:44,010 --> 00:31:47,110
Did Min Jun find out
that their fingerprints...

461
00:31:48,380 --> 00:31:49,450
are a match?

462
00:31:51,380 --> 00:31:52,680
How did you know about that?

463
00:31:57,520 --> 00:31:59,820
How could you possibly know
that Jin Ju's and Chloe's prints...

464
00:32:00,460 --> 00:32:01,520
are identical?

465
00:32:09,830 --> 00:32:12,800
Are you saying
you knew Chloe was Jin Ju?

466
00:32:19,340 --> 00:32:20,680
I asked you if you knew.

467
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:52,610
(Pearl in Red)

468
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:54,180
This is as far as I'll go.

469
00:32:54,180 --> 00:32:56,480
The rest is up to you, Mr. Park.

470
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:59,280
Of course. From now on,
I'll be the one deceiving Jin Ju.

471
00:32:59,420 --> 00:33:04,020
I'm doing whatever it takes
because I love you and want you,

472
00:33:04,290 --> 00:33:06,360
so why do you always have to stomp
on my heart?

473
00:33:06,620 --> 00:33:09,630
Love isn't about owning someone,
it's about being with them.

474
00:33:09,830 --> 00:33:12,160
What you're feeling isn't love.

475
00:33:12,260 --> 00:33:14,460
It's just greed and selfishness.

476
00:33:15,700 --> 00:33:17,700
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
